license; the list below is informational.

Major runtime dependencies:
  - Node.js 20 LTS (MIT)
  - Express 4 (MIT)
  - Drizzle ORM (Apache-2.0)
  - PostgreSQL 16 (PostgreSQL License)
  - Redis 7 (Redis Source Available License)
  - BullMQ (MIT)
  - argon2 (Apache-2.0)
  - Zod (MIT)
  - Pino (MIT)
  - pdfjs-dist (Apache-2.0)
  - pdf-parse (MIT)
  - pdf-lib (MIT, dev fixture only)
  - React 18 + ReactDOM (MIT)
  - TanStack Query 5 (MIT)
  - react-router 6 (MIT)
  - Tailwind CSS 3 (MIT)
  - Vite 5 (MIT)

External services (operator-managed):
  - GLM-OCR (Zhipu AI, MIT)
  - Vibe LLM Gateway (PolyForm Internal Use 1.0.0)

Optional services:
  - Anthropic Claude API (subject to Anthropic's terms;
    opt-in only, OFF by default — see ADR-019, ADR-020)

Data:
  - data/fidir/fidir-us.txt is a starter set of major US banks.
    The production deployment must replace it with the current Intuit
    publication. See data/fidir/README.md.
